description.1: The search for Mister Fantastic begins! Reed has been mysteriously abducted, and Susan, Johnny, and Ben will stop at nothing to find him! But who is behind this covert kidnapping?
description.2: Biker zombies? Alien prophets? Vampiric divas? It's Carnival time—X-Men style—when Wolverine hits Rio! Vacations are never fun for Logan. While visiting an old friend in Rio, the feral fan-favorite falls into a murder mystery which pits him against a creepy crew of killers! It's a festival of death at the height of Carnival—with Wolverine as the guest of honor!
description.3: The Gathering is drawing nigh! And one of the key participants, Override, has some last minute preparations to make!
description.8: In'the eight years'since'the fall'of the'Empire,'Luke Skywalker'has trained a new group'of'Jedi Knights, among them'the warrior woman'Kirana Ti, the sky-hermit'Streen, the scholar and lore-master'Tionne, and his greatest student, the brash'Kyp Durron. Once trained, a'Jedi'must go where he is needed, to defend the'New Republic'and use the'light side'of'the Force'to help those in need. On Coruscant, Chief of State Leia Organa Solo receives a desperate message from miners on the harsh world of Corbos. They have awakened something in their excavations and have come under attack. Luke sends Kyp Durron and the young clone Dorsk 82 to investigate and offer whatever assistance they can. But when Kyp and Dorsk 82 arrive on storm-swept Corbos, they find only an empty mining colony, and the scene of a terrible disaster.
description.9: On Rhen Var, the powerless, exiled Jedi Ulic Qel-Droma continues to train Vima. Sylvar, the ferocious Cathar Jedi, has gone into isolation herself, directing all her anger and energy toward thoughts of revenge aimed at Ulic. But when a messenger comes to her campfire, informing her that Vima Sunrider has vanished, she rushes to offer Nomi any help she can give.
description.10: As Rogue Squadron prepares for a nightmare showdown against Imperial fighters and ground troops, Isard begins her own personal war in the corridors of power on Imperial Center... a war fought with hidden bombs, double-crossing servants, and knives in the back!
description.16: For once, everything in Peter's life seems to be going all right! But you know what that means…something sinister is brewing in the shadows, and its last name is OSBORN!
description.18: In the wake of the'Emperor's'death'at the hands of'Luke Skywalker'and Darth Vader,'Mara Jade'has been captured! Since her captor is one of only a handful who knows she is the'Emperor's Hand, Mara knows she must escape quickly- or die!
description.22: Super-villain weapons dealer Devlin DeAngelo has gotten his hands on a broken Super-Adaptoid, and he kidnaps the only man that can repair it - Bruce Banner!
description.23: The saga of J2 begins! Zane Yama is a young man destined for a super powered life- after all...he is the son of the Unstoppable Juggernaut! Zane discovers his unusual abilities and super hero persona, in this jam-packed inaugural issue!
description.24: The Rhino buries Captain America under several tons of debris! Will he make it out alive?!
description.25: Who is she? Where did she come from? Spider-Girl is here and her super hero star is just rising!
description.26: Join the all-new adventure of May Parker, daughter of the 'infamous' Spider-Man, on her journey to finding herself as well as control over her powers -- powers that "Dad" has passed down to her!
description.27: The X-Men battle a strange yet oddly familiar group of mutants...
description.28: The Wendigo lies in wait as Wolverine returns to his old stomping grounds at a Weapon X facility.
description.30: Mister Fantastic - without the Fantastic Four! Reed Richards is ambushed alone by a group of mercenaries, including one of the FF's earliest foes...the Trapster!
description.34: Norman Osborn launches his next sinister scheme!
description.41: THE RETURN OF THE MOLTEN MAN! Spider-Man must save the civilians from the wrath of the Molten Man who is after Alison Mongrain.
description.44: Domino in danger! X-Force needs to rescue Domino before it’s too late!
description.49: Having barely escaped Spymaster, Iron Man's in no fighting form. But the return of the Mandarin has Tony heading into battle...and clinging onto life! Black Widow guest-stars.
description.50: Vima decides to search out Ulic herself.
description.51: The Rogues stage a dangerous rescue of Sate Pestage. Now is their chance to undermine Ysanne Isard, who has her own designs on the Imperial throne. But a power struggle in the Empire's highest circles has Isard cornered, and that's when the Imperial Intelligence Chief is most dangerous!
description.54: Madame Web has her own vision for Peter Parker’s life. And maybe an answer or two on how to deal with Green Goblin...
description.58: Under cover of an'Imperial'raid,'Mara Jade'infiltrates the headquarters of would-be'Black Nebula'overlord'Dequc, and'assassinates'the criminal leader. But back on'Imperial Center, she finds evidence that the person she shot was a stand-in, and that the real Dequc is still out there, and gunning for her!
description.59: A FLASH TO THE FUTURE! We get a glimpse of Spider-Man's future when two young archaeologists discover what once was Spider-Man's web shooter.
description.60: TWO HEROES, ONE CITY! Spider-Man and Daredevil use their heightened senses to take down Synario who has constructed virtual reality scenarios as a distraction while she steals.
description.61: This is it! Cable’s final stand against the terroristic Acolytes! Plus, Nathan’s techno organic virus has a dangerous flare-up…
description.62: One of the best friendships in all of Marvel is reunited at last! The Torch finds himself in the sights of Kraven the Hunter, but he won't have to face him alone! Look out, Kraven - here comes the Spider-Man!
description.63: X-Force only wants to enjoy their Hawaiian vacation but their tropical dream becomes a lava-filled nightmare when Risque shows up!
description.68: The Squadron Supreme returns to their home dimension after being held prisoner in an alternate universe! But what the team encounters upon their return threatens to undo all their heroic intent!
description.71: Whiplash and Spymaster are back! Iron Man's deadliest foes return to the super-criminal scene...and with deadlier, advanced tech! Plus, is this the end of Tony Stark's secret identity?
description.81: The Hulk goes stealth! A new Hulkbuster base has closely guarded secrets that Hulk needs to find out - so it's time for Bruce Banner to sneak in!
description.84: A unique Energy shield replaces Captain Ameerica's Triangular Replica shield that was damaged by the Lunatic Legion!
description.85: Rogue finally has her chance to be a human and the curse of her mutant powers lifted.  But can she allow this cure to exist when it can hurt those she loves?
description.86: Will Wolverine fall under the spell of the Hand and Hydra? Guest-starring Shadowcat and Sabretooth!
description.89: Vima vows to become a Jedi while Ulic debates on how to live the rest of his life.
description.96: After she fails to eliminate the young'Jedi'Luke Skywalker,'Mara Jade'is dispatched to take down a'crimelord'who seeks to'reestablish'the criminal organization'Black Sun. Little does she know that the'Emperor's imminent date with death will change her life forever!'
description.97: Their rest and relaxation over, Rogue Squadron and a Rebel task force descend on the world where Sate Pestage, one-time Emperor-proxy, has gone into exile. If the New Republic wants to claim Imperial Center for themselves and turn the tide of the war, it is imperative that they rescue Pestage, wanted by the Empire for high treason.

0.text: THE GOBLIN RETURNS! And this time, Spider-Man can't beat him alone -- thankfully an all-new SPIDER-WOMAN comes to the rescue!

4.text: The Six team up with the Fantastic Four to tackle the menace of The Moot…who knows Havok is not of this reality!

5.text: Doctor Druid suspects a doppelganger is acting on behalf of Adam Clayton. Plus, attack of the Lizard-Men!

6.text: Blade in the Big Easy! While “cruising” on a riverboat in the Bayou, Blade conflicts with a vampire who must be eviscerated! Plus, a new client!

7.text: After committing suicide, a demonic version of Punisher is reincarnated through a satanic life force! And he’s perpetuating a war between angels and demons…

13.text: The Avengers have made it to Magnum's floating resort with designs on taking him down! But will the help of Triathlon and Silverclaw be enough to give them the edge they need to win the day?

15.text: Deadpool prepares for his prophesized conflict with the alien menace Tiamat.

16.text: For once, everything in Peter's life seems to be going all right! But you know what that means…something sinister is brewing in the shadows, and its last name is OSBORN!

17.text: The Thunderbolts are back for more stunning action in the conclusion to their second story arc! The team is tasked with saving a town sieged by evil. Will the Thunderbolts save the day, and win back the public’s adoration?

19.text: In a flashback to 1942, things seem rather fishy when the Atlanteans and the Human Torch form alliances with the Nazis!

20.text: Back in the states, Daredevil is confronted with another one of Kingpin’s duplicitous schemes. In court, Murdock defends the ‘patsy’ hired to take the rap for Kingpin. In the streets, Daredevil foils Kingpin’s plot by taking down four of his worst enemies!

21.text: You are cordially invited to the wedding of Captain Britain and Meggan. As the couple begins a new chapter, has the book closed for Excalibur as a team?

29.text: Joe Kelly celebrates the 35th Anniversary of the X-Men! Witness the formation of an all-new mutant team. Plus, the mystery behind the ‘evil X-Men’ reaches a head.

31.text: Havok, hero and X-Man, awakens in a new reality…inside an alternate version reality of himself! And the X-Men he's surrounded by are very different from those back home. Enter The Six: Marvel Woman, Bloodstorm, The Fallen, Ice-Man and the Brute! How will Havok adjust to this new world with a much darker version of the X-Men at his side?

32.text: Can the Monster Hunters take down Gorgilla, AKA the horrific Missing Link?

33.text: A hit against a vampire mafia Don goes sideways when Blade accepts a contract from an untrustworthy source! Look out, Eric, you have THREE day walkers to slay!

35.text: Hawkeye is one of Earth's Mightiest Heroes, an upstanding member of the Avengers. Can he stop the villainy of Taskmaster all by himself?

36.text: THE SIEGE OF WUNDAGORE PART 3. The heroes fighting the High Evolutionary lie scattered and beaten, overcome by the strange creatures that only Wundagore can offer. Species die as quickly as they evolve in Wundagore; what will happen when Luke Cage and Iron Fist start to "evolve" into beasts?

37.text: THE SIEGE OF WUNDAGORE PART 5. In their climactic battle against the High Evolutionary and his hordes of half-beasts, the Heroes for Hire and the Knights of Wundagore face their greatest challenge yet! Will the heroes be able to destroy Isotope E, the strange substance responsible for their transformations? Plus, Bova proves she can hold her own in battle!

38.text: THE SIEGE OF WUNDAGORE PART 4. Quicksilver inhabits the power of Magneto! In a twist no Marvel fan will expect, Quicksilver uses his father’s powers over magnetism to escape the craggy heights of Wundagore Mountain. But how did Quicksilver come to acquire these abilities? The Heroes for Hire team-up with the Knights to take down Man-Beast and Exodus once and for all!

39.text: This volume continues the stories of the enigmatic Wolverine' gifted with heightened senses, a healing factor and razor-sharp claws' as he struggles to control his feral nature. Guest appearances by Jubilee and Rogue of the X-Men.

40.text:
New edition! These early classic Stan Lee/Jack Kirby adventures of Marvel's First Family - the Invisible Girl, the Human Torch, the Thing and Mr. Fantastic - defined the Marvel Age of Comics!
528 PGS./ALL AGES/BLACK & WHITE...$16.99

42.text: THE NEMESIS CONTRACT PART 1 Cable’s body continues to deteriorate from the techno-virus due to his lack of telepathy. With new threats on the horizon, will Cable train until he’s maxed out? Agent Jack Truman continues to dig up dirt on Cable, while Zzzax makes his presence known in Hell’s Kitchen! Can Cable defeat two foes in one fell swoop?

47.text: With his control over Mjolnir on the fritz, Thor faces death by drowning in his battle against Sedna! Plus, an appearance by Sub-Mariner!

54.text: Madame Web has her own vision for Peter Parker’s life. And maybe an answer or two on how to deal with Green Goblin...

55.text: Have the Thunderbolts reverted to their villainous ways? The pressure of being full time heroes catches up with the team, and allegiances shift. Abandoned by the media, and in the court of ill-favored public opinion, the Thunderbolts may have no choice but to drop the super hero gig and embrace the cloak of villainy!

56.text: Moses Magnum has attacked a major airport at the most inopportune time for the Avengers! With the help of Triathlon, can the Earth's Mightiest win the day? Plus, things heat up between the Scarlet Witch and the newly resurrected Wonder Man!

61.text: This is it! Cable’s final stand against the terroristic Acolytes! Plus, Nathan’s techno organic virus has a dangerous flare-up…

67.text: Now sharing space in the physical realm with a man named Jake, Thor must deal with the intricacies of mortal life. But when the sea goddess, Sedna, begins an aquatic rampage, the Odinson is called upon to save the day!

69.text: THE SIEGE OF WUNDAGORE PART 1. A tie-in event featuring the Heroes for Hire, Quicksilver, and the Knights of Wundagore! Bova, former nursemaid to Scarlet Witch and Quicksilver, informs the Knights that the High Evolutionary has undergone a disturbing transformation. Marvel’s mightiest flock to the mystical heights of Wundagore to investigate!

70.text: THE SIEGE OF WUNDAGORE PART 2. Upon his return to Haven, Quicksilver finds that the Heroes for Hire have undergone a disturbing transformation; the entire team has been turned into ape-like creatures! The High Evolutionary sets his teeth into his latest bounty in the second installment of Siege of Wundagore.

73.text: A night out at the opera becomes a psychotic (and emotional) murder attempt against Mister Fantastic! Good thing Cecilia Reyes and Beast took a night off from the X-Mansion and are at the same performance!

74.text: After receiving a distress signal from Moonglow, the Avengers set sail for Project Pegasus to find out who's responsible for the attack on the Squadron Supreme HQ.

75.text: Happy Hogan recounts a time when Tony Stark took down a secret agenda against Stark Industries as Iron Man.

76.text: Marvel Chiller! Several classic monsters, (styled by Jack Kirby from before Marvel’s Silver Age), are resurrected! Monster slayers Doc Druid, Jake Curtiss, Ulysses Bloodstone & Zawadi unite to take down these savage foes before humankind is stamped out!

77.text: IN THE FOLD PART 3 Danny Rand’s half-sister bursts on the scene, but not for a family reunion! Iron Fist vs. Death Sting in a kung fu duel to the death!

78.text: Captain America is propelled into an adventure happening just a few years into the future….and he also has himself a new girlfriend!

79.text: FLYING BLIND PART 4 Matt Murdock, reunited with his true self! During battle with Kingpin, Laurent Levasseur regains his memories of being Daredevil. His temporary sight fading, DD must also confront one ticked off Foggy Nelson!

80.text: Read this comic with one eye-closed as the mutants hit the town for the bachelor party of Captain Britain!

87.text: Mastermind tricks the X-Men into believing the Dark Phoenix has arisen once more!

88.text: The Green Goblin holds Spider-Man and Kingsley captive!

91.text: The Lunatic Legion is causing trouble on the moon! The Avengers head off-planet to stop them from powering their newest weapon. Plus, Warbird calls it quits!

95.text: Graviton rumbles back on the scene! Plus, an unusual battle ensues between Baron Zemo and Citizen V. Witness an old fashioned duel you have to read to believe!

98.text: IN THE FOLD PART 2 What is the Scorpio Key? What malign power does it contain? And if uncovered by the wrong hands, will Iron Fist be able to intervene? The next exciting chapter of In the Fold!

99.text: In this off-the-wall oneshot, Mojo of Mojoverse pits X-Baby against X-Bully in a game show of Arcade's making. Mojo TV will never look the same when the X-Babies enter Murderama!
